7
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:43,000
Choose which wallet signs. Here, Wallet 3.

8
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:48,500
Each wallet shows its real on-chain transaction history.

9
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:57,500
Connect actions like building blocks, data flows to the next step.

10
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:06,500
Casper Actions: send CSPR, stake, call contracts, anchor attestations,

11
00:01:07,500 --> 00:01:11,000
