15
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:35,000
One click, the AI builds the entire flow.

16
00:01:35,500 --> 00:01:39,000
Your agent is ready.

17
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:44,000
Running live on Casper testnet. Real, not simulated.

18
