The attestation, the AI's verdict, permanently anchored. Success.

23
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:17,500
Bring your own AI model, wallets and data sources.

24
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:22,500
Integrations: Casper, AI models, Telegram, Discord,

25
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:27,500
